      <p class="chro-body" style="margin-top:18px;max-width:44rem;">The next workforce is people and agents, side by side. AI doesn't replace your team &mdash; it makes the people who embrace it markedly more effective. OTP shows you who's growing, where to invest, and how to plan for both.</p>
